text: Jon Michael Reichenbach (born September 14, 1961 in Fort Meade, Maryland) is a former American football linebacker who played eight seasons in the National Football League, mainly with the Philadelphia Eagles. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:American football linebackers Category:Philadelphia Eagles players Category:Miami Dolphins players Category:East Stroudsburg Warriors football players Category:People from Fort Meade, Maryland
